WEBVTT

1
00:00:10.120 --> 00:00:11.328
THIS SERIES IS FICTITIOUS

2
00:00:11.329 --> 00:00:13.957
CHILDREN WERE FILMED SAFELY
GEN AI WAS USED IN SELECT SCENES

3
00:00:15.125 --> 00:00:17.042
{\an8}EPISODE 4

4
00:00:35.520 --> 00:00:36.688
{\an8}You're home.

5
00:00:39.232 --> 00:00:41.026
{\an8}Where were you all night?

6
00:00:42.027 --> 00:00:43.320
{\an8}Why are you out here?

7
00:00:43.945 --> 00:00:45.238
{\an8}You should be in bed.

8
00:00:46.948 --> 00:00:48.492
{\an8}You've been acting weird lately.

9
00:00:48.992 --> 00:00:51.036
You're always late.
and I can never reach you.

10
00:00:55.499 --> 00:00:56.541
Something came up.

11
00:00:57.542 --> 00:00:59.711
You couldn't even call me?

12
00:01:07.844 --> 00:01:08.845
Where's Hayun?

13
00:01:11.223 --> 00:01:14.601
She kept asking for you
then fell asleep a while ago.

14
00:01:15.769 --> 00:01:16.770
Right.

15
00:01:21.691 --> 00:01:23.485
What could possibly keep you out so late?

16
00:01:26.655 --> 00:01:29.282
I told you.
something came up at the hospital.

17
00:01:33.787 --> 00:01:34.913
Honey.

18
00:01:36.456 --> 00:01:37.958
Are you hiding something from me?

19
00:01:41.002 --> 00:01:42.170
I'm not.

20
00:01:45.423 --> 00:01:47.133
You sure there's nothing going on?

21
00:01:50.345 --> 00:01:51.346
I'm sure.

22
00:01:53.765 --> 00:01:55.100
Fine.

23
00:01:58.228 --> 00:01:59.479
Listen.

24
00:02:00.480 --> 00:02:01.648
I'm your wife.

25
00:02:03.233 --> 00:02:07.028
You have to tell me
if there is something going on.

26
00:02:07.696 --> 00:02:11.532
I can tell you're having a hard time.
but you won't say anything.

27
00:02:19.040 --> 00:02:20.041
Okay.

28
00:02:21.209 --> 00:02:24.004
I just hope
there's really nothing going on.

29
00:02:29.009 --> 00:02:30.510
But can I just say something?

30
00:02:31.094 --> 00:02:32.804
You've changed so much.

31
00:02:34.431 --> 00:02:36.433
I barely recognize you anymore.

32
00:02:48.528 --> 00:02:49.988
Where's your wedding ring?

33
00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:55.327
I took it off before surgery.
I probably left it in the office.

34
00:03:16.806 --> 00:03:18.932
ACCESS RESTRICTED

35
00:03:18.933 --> 00:03:20.309
ACCESS GRANTED

36
00:03:20.310 --> 00:03:24.898
{\an8}RESTRICTED ACCESS
AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY

37
00:03:56.971 --> 00:03:57.972
Geez. you scared me.

38
00:03:58.390 --> 00:03:59.890
What are you doing here so late?

39
00:03:59.891 --> 00:04:01.975
You know.
I just left something in the office.

40
00:04:01.976 --> 00:04:05.104
Must be pretty damn important.

41
00:04:05.105 --> 00:04:06.897
Hang in there. then. See you.

42
00:04:06.898 --> 00:04:07.899
Okay.

43
00:04:09.484 --> 00:04:10.485
Chiung.

44
00:04:11.569 --> 00:04:12.653
Yes?

45
00:04:12.654 --> 00:04:14.531
What? You got something to say?

46
00:04:15.323 --> 00:04:17.282
The thing is…

47
00:04:17.283 --> 00:04:19.035
Sorry. let me take this real quick.

48
00:04:20.078 --> 00:04:21.286
This is Choi.

49
00:04:21.287 --> 00:04:23.997
Dr. Choi. it's me.
I'll cut right to the chase.

50
00:04:23.998 --> 00:04:27.626
- Have you heard from Taeju at all?
- Yeah. what a coincidence.

51
00:04:27.627 --> 00:04:29.086
Are you with him right now?

52
00:04:29.087 --> 00:04:30.295
Yes.

53
00:04:30.296 --> 00:04:32.881
The police are on their way.

54
00:04:32.882 --> 00:04:35.467
so you have to keep him there.
no matter what.

55
00:04:35.468 --> 00:04:36.928
Yeah. I got it.

56
00:04:41.599 --> 00:04:43.851
Chiung. I'm so sorry.

57
00:04:43.852 --> 00:04:45.352
I'll explain later!

58
00:04:53.153 --> 00:04:55.279
RED LIGHT AND SPEEDING
SURVEILLANCE CAMERA

59
00:04:57.157 --> 00:04:59.199
Captain. we got an update
on Kang's location.

60
00:04:59.200 --> 00:05:00.284
Where?

61
00:05:00.285 --> 00:05:03.412
He was at Deoksam Intersection
at 9:46 p.m.

62
00:05:03.413 --> 00:05:04.414
Heading that way.

63
00:05:15.049 --> 00:05:18.260
Plate number 1228. please pull over.

64
00:05:18.261 --> 00:05:19.678
Pull over. 1228.

65
00:05:24.601 --> 00:05:27.019
Suspect vehicle is heading
toward Shinyu-dong.

66
00:05:27.020 --> 00:05:29.230
Units two and three. in pursuit.

67
00:05:36.321 --> 00:05:37.655
Kang Taeju!

68
00:05:38.156 --> 00:05:39.991
Pull over right now!

69
00:05:40.700 --> 00:05:42.284
Stop being so reckless!

70
00:05:42.285 --> 00:05:43.953
Cut him off! Get in front of him!

71
00:05:45.079 --> 00:05:46.706
Damn it.

72
00:06:05.266 --> 00:06:06.642
Turn around! Step on it!

73
00:06:06.643 --> 00:06:10.730
Control. we lost the suspect
vehicle during pursuit. Plate number 1228.

74
00:07:26.014 --> 00:07:27.889
Everyone. back up!

75
00:07:27.890 --> 00:07:29.100
Keep them away!

76
00:07:37.942 --> 00:07:40.319
Captain. it looks like he went
toward the main road.

77
00:07:40.320 --> 00:07:42.238
Go after him. He couldn't have gone far.

78
00:07:58.921 --> 00:08:00.673
{\an8}SEONGJIN POLICE STATION

79
00:08:14.187 --> 00:08:17.856
TAKING ACCOUNTABILITY
FOR THE PEOPLE

80
00:08:17.857 --> 00:08:20.610
SEONGJIN POLICE STATION

81
00:08:34.916 --> 00:08:36.626
Hey. stop!

82
00:08:39.087 --> 00:08:41.463
- Kang Taeju is over there!
- Back up!

83
00:08:41.464 --> 00:08:44.800
We found Kang Taeju. He's over there!

84
00:08:53.267 --> 00:08:54.268
Go!

85
00:08:57.939 --> 00:08:59.273
- That way!
- Yes. sir!

86
00:09:12.620 --> 00:09:13.996
Get to the second floor. now!

87
00:09:13.997 --> 00:09:15.039
Yes. sir.

88
00:09:21.421 --> 00:09:22.796
Where did he go?

89
00:09:22.797 --> 00:09:25.049
Go the other way! Block him off!

90
00:09:30.346 --> 00:09:32.640
What the hell. man? Stop!

91
00:09:33.182 --> 00:09:35.100
What the hell are you doing?

92
00:09:35.101 --> 00:09:36.227
Get him!

93
00:09:37.186 --> 00:09:39.022
Hey! Wait. Kang Taeju!

94
00:09:46.404 --> 00:09:47.863
- He's moving!
- That nutjob.

95
00:09:47.864 --> 00:09:49.573
Kang Taeju. stop!

96
00:09:49.574 --> 00:09:50.658
Kang Taeju!

97
00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:52.826
Chase him down!

98
00:09:52.827 --> 00:09:53.910
- Hey. Kim.
- Sir?

99
00:09:53.911 --> 00:09:56.080
- Request backup ASAP!
- Yes. sir.

100
00:09:59.625 --> 00:10:01.835
Copy. Seongjin PD request for backup.

101
00:10:01.836 --> 00:10:03.920
Two patrol units rolling immediately.

102
00:10:03.921 --> 00:10:06.424
Detective unit to follow.

103
00:11:00.686 --> 00:11:02.063
Seyun.

104
00:11:09.278 --> 00:11:10.404
Let's put an end to this.

105
00:11:11.280 --> 00:11:12.281
What?

106
00:11:14.450 --> 00:11:15.576
I want a divorce.

107
00:11:18.704 --> 00:11:20.289
That bastard.

108
00:11:24.127 --> 00:11:27.630
My gosh! What was that?

109
00:11:52.572 --> 00:11:53.989
Move!

110
00:11:53.990 --> 00:11:54.991
Over there!

111
00:11:58.161 --> 00:11:59.328
That way.

112
00:12:23.144 --> 00:12:24.312
There you are.

113
00:12:31.277 --> 00:12:34.572
You think you can play games with cops?
You have the right to an attorney...

114
00:12:36.616 --> 00:12:37.949
No!

115
00:13:01.599 --> 00:13:02.934
No…

116
00:13:12.485 --> 00:13:13.736
Kang Taeju…

117
00:13:17.573 --> 00:13:19.075
You can't move your arms and legs?

118
00:13:20.534 --> 00:13:24.037
Your spinal cord is damaged.

119
00:13:24.038 --> 00:13:26.916
You'll damage your nerves permanently
if you try to move.

120
00:13:48.562 --> 00:13:49.939
Don't move. okay?

121
00:14:00.783 --> 00:14:01.867
Hold on…

122
00:14:08.207 --> 00:14:09.291
There you go.

123
00:14:18.676 --> 00:14:20.302
Hello. we need an ambulance.

124
00:14:21.303 --> 00:14:24.389
Yeah. I'm at Ilseo Supply Center.

125
00:14:24.390 --> 00:14:28.019
There's a patient with spinal cord damage
in the stairwell down to the basement.

126
00:14:29.103 --> 00:14:32.314
Yeah. he needs to get to a hospital. STAT.
So please hurry.

127
00:15:06.432 --> 00:15:11.353
THE HUSBAND

128
00:15:15.816 --> 00:15:18.485
EMERGENCY SERVICES

129
00:15:18.486 --> 00:15:21.197
- Hey. Kim. You all right?
- Wait. hold on.

130
00:15:21.697 --> 00:15:24.200
Captain. Kang Taeju…

131
00:15:24.867 --> 00:15:26.367
He took my gun.

132
00:15:26.368 --> 00:15:27.620
Your gun?

133
00:15:28.245 --> 00:15:29.371
I'm sorry. sir.

134
00:15:34.752 --> 00:15:37.504
All right.
Don't worry about that right now.

135
00:15:37.505 --> 00:15:39.173
Please take him to the hospital.

136
00:15:44.470 --> 00:15:46.930
Hey. will he be okay?

137
00:15:46.931 --> 00:15:49.682
Well. we can't be sure
until we get to the hospital.

138
00:15:49.683 --> 00:15:54.021
but thanks to the prompt first aid.
I think he'll be able to avoid the worst.

139
00:15:57.316 --> 00:15:58.400
First aid?

140
00:16:02.446 --> 00:16:04.030
Hey. put out an APB on Kang Taeju.

141
00:16:04.031 --> 00:16:05.032
- I'm on it.
- Yes. sir.

142
00:16:52.204 --> 00:16:57.877
EUMGOK. JUNSEONG

143
00:17:05.342 --> 00:17:08.179
The doors are closing.

144
00:17:08.929 --> 00:17:13.684
THIS TRAIN IS BOUND FOR JUNSEONG

145
00:17:52.181 --> 00:17:54.266
I'm impressed. Kang Taeju.

146
00:18:01.857 --> 00:18:03.651
You actually made it.

147
00:18:05.611 --> 00:18:07.029
Where's my wife right now?

148
00:18:08.489 --> 00:18:09.490
Come with me.

149
00:18:29.468 --> 00:18:33.639
NAMGANG LIVESTOCK DISTRIBUTION

150
00:19:24.273 --> 00:19:25.441
Where are we?

151
00:19:26.859 --> 00:19:29.902
I thought we were going to find my wife.

152
00:19:29.903 --> 00:19:33.114
That's for you
to figure out from here on out.

153
00:19:33.115 --> 00:19:34.158
Excuse me?

154
00:19:38.829 --> 00:19:40.456
Is this some kind of joke?

155
00:19:41.915 --> 00:19:44.627
You said you knew
I didn't have my wife kidnapped.

156
00:19:45.711 --> 00:19:48.505
You said you'd help me find her.
So where is she right now?

157
00:19:54.678 --> 00:19:56.847
{\an8}NEUROSURGEON KANG TAEJU

158
00:19:58.515 --> 00:20:00.517
SEYUN

159
00:20:08.609 --> 00:20:09.610
What the hell?

160
00:20:10.402 --> 00:20:11.945
Are you working with that bastard?

161
00:20:12.571 --> 00:20:13.739
Where is my wife?

162
00:20:15.824 --> 00:20:17.326
Answer me!

163
00:20:18.369 --> 00:20:19.453
I told you.

164
00:20:20.412 --> 00:20:22.288
It's up to you to figure it out now.

165
00:20:22.289 --> 00:20:23.332
What?

166
00:20:24.208 --> 00:20:25.458
Are you kidding me?

167
00:20:25.459 --> 00:20:27.627
Do you want to die right here?

168
00:20:27.628 --> 00:20:29.046
Where's Seyun?

169
00:20:32.341 --> 00:20:34.885
Where is Seyun? Where is she?

170
00:20:36.011 --> 00:20:37.888
Have you ever killed a person before?

171
00:20:39.223 --> 00:20:40.224
What?

172
00:20:41.141 --> 00:20:43.935
You must have had
your opportunities as a doctor.

173
00:20:43.936 --> 00:20:47.189
There's only a fine line
between saving a life and taking one.

174
00:20:48.941 --> 00:20:50.317
What the hell are you saying?

175
00:20:51.110 --> 00:20:55.114
How far will Kang Taeju go for his wife?

176
00:20:57.908 --> 00:21:00.119
Could he kill a person?

177
00:21:35.571 --> 00:21:36.572
Say hi.

178
00:21:37.614 --> 00:21:38.615
That's my wife.

179
00:21:42.745 --> 00:21:44.496
If you can't find the bastard soon.

180
00:21:45.831 --> 00:21:47.791
your wife will end up like her too.

181
00:21:51.587 --> 00:21:54.256
That's why you're going to be my bait.

182
00:21:55.841 --> 00:21:57.468
You get your wife back.

183
00:21:59.303 --> 00:22:00.721
and I get to kill the bastard.

184
00:22:09.521 --> 00:22:11.190
What. so that's your wife?

185
00:22:15.235 --> 00:22:16.487
What does that even…

186
00:22:22.493 --> 00:22:24.118
PARK GYEONGMIN

187
00:22:24.119 --> 00:22:25.662
OCCUPATION
PHOTOGRAPHY INSTRUCTOR

188
00:22:46.016 --> 00:22:47.309
You know. you're right.

189
00:22:48.685 --> 00:22:51.188
There's a fine line
between saving a life and taking one.

190
00:22:52.648 --> 00:22:54.066
That's the trade I'm in.

191
00:22:55.359 --> 00:22:57.110
It demands absolute precision.

192
00:22:58.195 --> 00:23:01.865
A tenth of a millimeter can
either kill or save a person.

193
00:23:02.407 --> 00:23:04.868
One nick to the brain stem
and they're dead on the table.

194
00:23:08.163 --> 00:23:09.580
Catch the spinal nerve root.

195
00:23:09.581 --> 00:23:14.294
and they're looking at
a lifetime of intractable. burning pain.

196
00:23:17.422 --> 00:23:18.632
Look. man.

197
00:23:21.635 --> 00:23:25.680
I don't care who's in that picture.
whether it's your wife or not.

198
00:23:25.681 --> 00:23:27.307
I only care about one thing.

199
00:23:30.269 --> 00:23:31.812
Where's my wife?

200
00:23:52.207 --> 00:23:55.335
What was that?

201
00:23:56.253 --> 00:23:58.255
What on earth is going on?

202
00:24:57.356 --> 00:24:58.357
Hello?

203
00:24:59.358 --> 00:25:00.691
Hello? Are you in here?

204
00:25:00.692 --> 00:25:03.527
How did you get out?

205
00:25:03.528 --> 00:25:05.656
No time to explain.
We have to get out of here.

206
00:25:12.412 --> 00:25:14.080
Why won't this thing open?

207
00:25:14.081 --> 00:25:16.375
- What? It won't open?
- No. it's…

208
00:25:18.251 --> 00:25:20.294
I think I'll need the keys to this door.

209
00:25:20.295 --> 00:25:22.129
Just save yourself while you can.

210
00:25:22.130 --> 00:25:24.341
No. I can't just leave you. Just hang on.

211
00:25:44.695 --> 00:25:46.154
I found the keys. Hold on.

212
00:25:46.780 --> 00:25:48.699
What? Really?

213
00:25:49.783 --> 00:25:50.909
Not this one.

214
00:25:52.703 --> 00:25:54.079
Come on.

215
00:25:54.913 --> 00:25:55.997
- Please.
- Oh. no.

216
00:25:55.998 --> 00:25:58.333
I don't think I stand a chance.

217
00:25:59.459 --> 00:26:02.212
Just get out of here.
You have to save yourself.

218
00:26:03.255 --> 00:26:06.425
Don't give up. You have to see
how your husband really feels.

219
00:26:17.019 --> 00:26:18.477
Got it.

220
00:26:30.407 --> 00:26:31.408
Ms. Ko.

221
00:26:33.702 --> 00:26:34.911
Where are you going?

222
00:26:51.553 --> 00:26:54.973
The things you go through
because of your husband…

223
00:26:56.600 --> 00:26:57.809
Am I right?

224
00:27:04.316 --> 00:27:06.610
LEE SUHYEONG
NATIONAL POLICE AGENCY

225
00:27:36.598 --> 00:27:37.599
Tell me.

226
00:27:39.309 --> 00:27:40.477
Who really are you?

227
00:27:42.729 --> 00:27:44.147
Why did you come looking for me?

228
00:27:46.274 --> 00:27:47.359
Six years ago.

229
00:27:49.236 --> 00:27:50.654
my wife was abducted.

230
00:27:55.951 --> 00:27:57.369
Just like your wife.

231
00:27:58.787 --> 00:28:00.120
SUSPECT INTERROGATION REPORT

232
00:28:00.121 --> 00:28:03.207
Yuseok. I'm going to ask you
one last time.

233
00:28:03.208 --> 00:28:05.292
Where did you hide
the rest of the merchandise?

234
00:28:05.293 --> 00:28:07.795
I don't know. How am I supposed to know?

235
00:28:07.796 --> 00:28:09.631
{\an8}INCOMING CALL
GYEONGMIN

236
00:28:10.215 --> 00:28:13.425
If you keep playing dumb
after I come back from this call.

237
00:28:13.426 --> 00:28:15.302
you'll be dead tonight.

238
00:28:15.303 --> 00:28:17.221
Be smart about this. Geez.

239
00:28:20.767 --> 00:28:22.268
Hey. honey. Don't wait up.

240
00:28:22.269 --> 00:28:24.478
I don't think I can make it home today.

241
00:28:24.479 --> 00:28:26.314
Detective Lee Suhyeong?

242
00:28:31.403 --> 00:28:32.528
Yeah. who's this?

243
00:28:32.529 --> 00:28:35.073
And why do you have my wife's phone?

244
00:28:39.536 --> 00:28:41.746
GYEONGMIN

245
00:28:47.168 --> 00:28:48.544
What the hell?

246
00:28:48.545 --> 00:28:49.880
Keep it down.

247
00:28:50.881 --> 00:28:54.843
If the cops around you catch on.
I'll have no choice but to kill her.

248
00:28:59.306 --> 00:29:01.432
What do you want from me?

249
00:29:01.433 --> 00:29:03.018
Thirty million won in cash.

250
00:29:03.643 --> 00:29:06.812
In one hour. meet me
at Yeongjin Industrial Complex. alone.

251
00:29:26.666 --> 00:29:27.750
Yeah.

252
00:29:27.751 --> 00:29:29.210
You see the door in front of you?

253
00:29:29.878 --> 00:29:31.630
Leave the money there and walk away.

254
00:29:32.881 --> 00:29:36.800
- And my wife?
- I'll tell you where she is in 10 minutes.

255
00:29:52.817 --> 00:29:53.985
Where is she?

256
00:29:55.695 --> 00:29:56.947
Where is my wife?

257
00:30:00.283 --> 00:30:01.409
Tell me!

258
00:30:02.077 --> 00:30:04.037
Honey.

259
00:30:04.746 --> 00:30:05.955
Gyeongmin.

260
00:30:08.375 --> 00:30:10.542
You're okay. right? You all right?

261
00:30:10.543 --> 00:30:11.752
I don't know.

262
00:30:11.753 --> 00:30:13.088
You're not hurt. are you?

263
00:30:14.339 --> 00:30:16.424
I'm just really dizzy.

264
00:30:17.509 --> 00:30:21.262
Honey. what's going to happen to me?

265
00:30:24.265 --> 00:30:25.892
You're going to be fine.

266
00:30:27.435 --> 00:30:29.020
Just give me a minute.

267
00:30:31.439 --> 00:30:32.857
I'll be right there.

268
00:30:33.358 --> 00:30:35.025
Hey. Detective.

269
00:30:35.026 --> 00:30:38.446
I think I made a huge mistake.

270
00:30:39.739 --> 00:30:40.823
What do you mean?

271
00:30:40.824 --> 00:30:46.453
Knowing how much you love your
wife. 30 million isn't going to cut it.

272
00:30:46.454 --> 00:30:48.789
I should have asked
for at least 100 million.

273
00:30:48.790 --> 00:30:50.792
What the hell are you talking about?

274
00:30:52.043 --> 00:30:53.460
We had an agreement.

275
00:30:53.461 --> 00:30:57.882
Get me the additional 70 million
by 1 p.m.. 2 days from now.

276
00:30:58.758 --> 00:31:00.759
Listen. you prick.

277
00:31:00.760 --> 00:31:02.177
Insult me all you want.

278
00:31:02.178 --> 00:31:04.221
but after you get me the money.

279
00:31:20.155 --> 00:31:26.452
JANUARY 31

280
00:31:32.375 --> 00:31:33.876
What took you so long?

281
00:31:33.877 --> 00:31:35.002
Where's my wife?

282
00:31:35.003 --> 00:31:36.504
I'm sorry. Detective.

283
00:31:37.130 --> 00:31:39.214
Something urgent came up.

284
00:31:39.215 --> 00:31:41.175
Leave the money by the pavilion.

285
00:31:41.176 --> 00:31:43.802
and I'll tell you
where she is in 10 minutes.

286
00:32:11.247 --> 00:32:12.956
{\an8}8:15 P.M.. JANUARY 31

287
00:32:12.957 --> 00:32:15.085
{\an8}8:16 P.M.. JANUARY 31

288
00:32:40.318 --> 00:32:42.946
Hello? What's going on here?

289
00:32:43.780 --> 00:32:45.657
I got you the money as promised.

290
00:32:47.325 --> 00:32:50.744
You should let my wife go now.

291
00:32:50.745 --> 00:32:51.954
I know.

292
00:32:51.955 --> 00:32:54.289
I totally should let her go.

293
00:32:54.290 --> 00:32:58.128
But the thing is.
I don't think I'll be able to.

294
00:32:59.712 --> 00:33:01.297
What are you talking about?

295
00:33:02.549 --> 00:33:06.677
You asked for more money.
so I brought it for you.

296
00:33:06.678 --> 00:33:08.179
Tell me about it.

297
00:33:08.847 --> 00:33:10.348
Why are you doing this?

298
00:33:11.683 --> 00:33:14.184
What's the reason?

299
00:33:14.185 --> 00:33:18.523
Detective. do you really not know
why I'm doing this?

300
00:33:20.400 --> 00:33:23.277
You're being punished for your wrongdoing.

301
00:33:23.278 --> 00:33:25.071
I'm so sorry. sir.

302
00:33:27.490 --> 00:33:29.825
I'm down on my knees
apologizing right now.

303
00:33:29.826 --> 00:33:31.410
I'm really sorry.

304
00:33:31.411 --> 00:33:35.289
What I've done is unacceptable. I'm sorry!

305
00:33:35.290 --> 00:33:37.040
But could you please…

306
00:33:37.041 --> 00:33:40.878
Could you please let my wife go?

307
00:33:40.879 --> 00:33:42.337
I'm begging you.

308
00:33:42.338 --> 00:33:43.964
So go ahead.

309
00:33:43.965 --> 00:33:45.592
Tell me what you've done wrong.

310
00:33:48.553 --> 00:33:50.554
Why apologize when you don't know?

311
00:33:50.555 --> 00:33:51.556
Detective.

312
00:33:53.057 --> 00:33:54.225
Just know this.

313
00:33:55.226 --> 00:33:57.061
What happened to your wife

314
00:33:59.022 --> 00:34:00.607
is all on you.

315
00:34:02.233 --> 00:34:04.526
Sir. please.

316
00:34:04.527 --> 00:34:05.570
Hello?

317
00:34:06.196 --> 00:34:07.197
Hello?

318
00:34:07.780 --> 00:34:09.115
Sir. please!

319
00:34:22.378 --> 00:34:25.757
And I got my wife back as a lifeless body.

320
00:34:31.471 --> 00:34:32.680
So you're saying…

321
00:34:33.640 --> 00:34:34.891
Yeah. it's him.

322
00:34:36.017 --> 00:34:38.520
The same man you're hunting right now.

323
00:34:39.312 --> 00:34:42.065
Since that day.
he's all I've thought about.

324
00:34:42.815 --> 00:34:45.109
The only reason
I'm still breathing is to catch him.

325
00:34:46.653 --> 00:34:51.032
And then. one day.
I heard his voice again.

326
00:35:12.845 --> 00:35:13.930
Hello?

327
00:35:14.430 --> 00:35:16.473
Where are you. Mr. Kang?

328
00:35:16.474 --> 00:35:19.810
Oh. I'm at my in-laws' house right now.

329
00:35:19.811 --> 00:35:20.894
In-laws?

330
00:35:20.895 --> 00:35:24.524
They managed to prepare the money.

331
00:35:25.942 --> 00:35:26.943
Listen to me.

332
00:35:27.485 --> 00:35:30.655
You're going to pay
for disappointing me until the end.

333
00:35:31.197 --> 00:35:33.866
You didn't keep up
your end of the deal. boss.

334
00:35:34.409 --> 00:35:36.160
And now. your wife's going to die.

335
00:35:39.914 --> 00:35:43.083
You didn't keep up
your end of the deal. boss.

336
00:35:43.084 --> 00:35:44.710
And now. your wife's going to die.

337
00:35:44.711 --> 00:35:47.088
Hey. Kang Taeju.

338
00:35:48.464 --> 00:35:49.632
This is on you.

339
00:35:52.594 --> 00:35:53.595
Detective.

340
00:35:55.054 --> 00:35:56.514
Just know this.

341
00:35:57.849 --> 00:35:59.684
What happened to your wife

342
00:36:01.102 --> 00:36:02.729
is all on you.

343
00:36:07.817 --> 00:36:09.902
It was the same voice…

344
00:36:16.534 --> 00:36:18.536
The same cadence and tone…

345
00:36:20.747 --> 00:36:22.498
from six years ago.

346
00:36:36.763 --> 00:36:38.096
These are the internal files

347
00:36:38.097 --> 00:36:40.850
on the two cases
that bastard pulled before.

348
00:36:46.689 --> 00:36:49.108
One's the murder of my wife.

349
00:36:50.151 --> 00:36:52.654
The other is a case
we suspect he's behind.

350
00:36:54.155 --> 00:36:58.242
The Seokdong Lake kidnapping
and murder from five years ago.

351
00:37:10.296 --> 00:37:12.172
ESTIMATED T.O.D.
37-38 HRS AFTER RANSOM CALL

352
00:37:12.173 --> 00:37:13.549
Exact same MO.

353
00:37:16.678 --> 00:37:23.643
His window for murder is
36 to 38 hours post-ransom call.

354
00:37:24.477 --> 00:37:28.855
It's already been 15 hours
since he took your wife.

355
00:37:28.856 --> 00:37:32.735
Why do you think he kidnapped her?

356
00:37:34.070 --> 00:37:35.071
Beats me.

357
00:37:35.905 --> 00:37:37.699
Who knows what this guy is thinking?

358
00:37:39.492 --> 00:37:41.494
But one thing is for sure.

359
00:37:42.995 --> 00:37:45.289
Your wife is still alive.

360
00:37:46.082 --> 00:37:47.792
Though she doesn't have much time left.

361
00:37:54.590 --> 00:37:56.676
So what do I have to do now

362
00:37:57.301 --> 00:37:59.053
to save my wife?

363
00:38:00.763 --> 00:38:02.181
First. you lure him out.

364
00:38:02.849 --> 00:38:04.851
But I don't even know where he is.

365
00:38:06.602 --> 00:38:08.438
You're going to cut him a deal.

366
00:38:09.605 --> 00:38:12.482
At around 10:20 p.m.
at Ilseo Industrial Complex.

367
00:38:12.483 --> 00:38:13.567
a standoff erupted

368
00:38:13.568 --> 00:38:15.652
between police and a neurosurgeon…

369
00:38:15.653 --> 00:38:19.656
…suspected of orchestrating
his wife's kidnapping and murder.

370
00:38:19.657 --> 00:38:21.908
The suspect disarmed an officer…

371
00:38:21.909 --> 00:38:22.910
Mr. Kang?

372
00:38:24.287 --> 00:38:25.370
He's good.

373
00:38:25.371 --> 00:38:28.623
He may have slipped into nearby
residential or busy commercial districts.

374
00:38:28.624 --> 00:38:30.835
Citizens are urged
to exercise extreme caution.

375
00:39:32.647 --> 00:39:34.106
{\an8}TUESDAY. FEBRUARY 10
ALARM

376
00:41:01.986 --> 00:41:04.654
Hey. are you ready?

377
00:41:04.655 --> 00:41:08.533
Punish me. O Great Spirit.
for I have sinned.

378
00:41:08.534 --> 00:41:11.369
I vowed to serve
and follow you and you only.

379
00:41:11.370 --> 00:41:14.706
Yet. I was foolish enough
to seek another deity.

380
00:41:14.707 --> 00:41:17.709
Please punish me.
for death is the only way...

381
00:41:22.673 --> 00:41:23.757
No.

382
00:41:23.758 --> 00:41:26.760
No.

383
00:41:26.761 --> 00:41:28.094
No!

384
00:41:28.095 --> 00:41:29.179
Stop it!

385
00:41:29.180 --> 00:41:31.848
No! Don't do it!

386
00:41:31.849 --> 00:41:33.683
Please don't do this!

387
00:41:33.684 --> 00:41:38.856
Please don't do this. please!

388
00:41:43.235 --> 00:41:44.236
Ms. Lee Seonja?

389
00:41:45.571 --> 00:41:46.906
Please say something.

390
00:41:48.699 --> 00:41:50.701
Please say something. Ms. Lee.

391
00:41:55.456 --> 00:41:56.623
Ms. Lee…

392
00:41:59.043 --> 00:42:01.670
Screw you. you sick freak!

393
00:42:01.671 --> 00:42:02.921
Just kill me!

394
00:42:02.922 --> 00:42:04.506
Kill me too!

395
00:42:24.235 --> 00:42:26.861
Hey. Captain.
Looking at the surveillance footage.

396
00:42:26.862 --> 00:42:29.280
it looks like after Kang
fled the industrial complex.

397
00:42:29.281 --> 00:42:33.159
he entered a nearby subway station.
got off at Shinyu Station.

398
00:42:33.160 --> 00:42:35.870
and then headed toward
the open lot right by the underpass.

399
00:42:35.871 --> 00:42:39.290
But there are no cameras
from the underpass to the lot.

400
00:42:39.291 --> 00:42:40.793
so we lost him here.

401
00:42:41.335 --> 00:42:43.211
Yeah. we're sweeping the perimeter.

402
00:42:43.212 --> 00:42:46.381
but with all the blind spots
and the outdated cameras in this area.

403
00:42:46.382 --> 00:42:48.718
we still can't lock down his exact route.

404
00:42:49.635 --> 00:42:52.555
- Go back to the footage from the station.
- Yes. sir.

405
00:42:55.975 --> 00:42:57.934
He definitely went there to meet someone.

406
00:42:57.935 --> 00:43:00.771
When perps are on the run. they just run.

407
00:43:01.313 --> 00:43:03.315
They don't stop to look at maps.

408
00:43:04.817 --> 00:43:08.988
It's possible he's got another accomplice
who knows where the blind spots are.

409
00:43:09.655 --> 00:43:10.656
Another accomplice?

410
00:43:11.949 --> 00:43:14.909
Check if any
of the local residents are ex-convicts.

411
00:43:14.910 --> 00:43:16.620
They likely left together in a vehicle.

412
00:43:17.371 --> 00:43:20.248
Oh. and pull every plate captured
within a five-kilometer radius

413
00:43:20.249 --> 00:43:22.500
at this hour and run background checks.

414
00:43:22.501 --> 00:43:24.085
- Yes. sir.
- We're on it.

415
00:43:24.086 --> 00:43:26.379
{\an8}Police have released
citizen footage showing

416
00:43:26.380 --> 00:43:29.090
{\an8}Kang brandishing a weapon
and terrorizing bystanders.

417
00:43:29.091 --> 00:43:31.551
We got to run!

418
00:43:31.552 --> 00:43:33.219
Dude. I think he's crazy.

419
00:43:33.220 --> 00:43:36.056
Officials say Kang is armed
and extremely unstable…

420
00:43:36.057 --> 00:43:38.641
Geez. that damn psycho.

421
00:43:38.642 --> 00:43:41.227
He's going to burn in hell.

422
00:44:02.166 --> 00:44:05.795
Geez. give me a break already.

423
00:44:20.184 --> 00:44:24.355
What are you…

424
00:44:25.064 --> 00:44:26.732
Let's step inside. Father.

425
00:44:30.111 --> 00:44:31.529
Honey. what's going on?

426
00:44:32.113 --> 00:44:33.114
Everything okay?

427
00:44:36.242 --> 00:44:39.536
Are you out of your mind?
How dare you point a gun at me!

428
00:44:39.537 --> 00:44:40.538
Step inside.

429
00:44:41.288 --> 00:44:42.706
Taeju.

430
00:44:43.707 --> 00:44:44.708
What…

431
00:44:47.086 --> 00:44:48.087
Where's Seyun?

432
00:44:49.588 --> 00:44:51.423
Where is she right now?

433
00:44:52.424 --> 00:44:53.801
Don't move. Mother.

434
00:44:55.052 --> 00:44:56.679
I can't tell you anything right now.

435
00:44:57.847 --> 00:44:59.306
What do you want then?

436
00:45:00.015 --> 00:45:02.393
Why the hell are you here with a gun?

437
00:45:03.894 --> 00:45:04.895
To pick up the money.

438
00:45:05.563 --> 00:45:07.356
What? Money?

439
00:45:08.315 --> 00:45:09.984
The three billion you have here.

440
00:45:10.901 --> 00:45:12.861
I need you to hand it over to me.

441
00:45:12.862 --> 00:45:14.363
You're going to cut him a deal.

442
00:45:14.989 --> 00:45:16.114
What?

443
00:45:16.115 --> 00:45:19.577
But before you do that. you have
to let him know you've got the money.

444
00:45:20.536 --> 00:45:24.998
"A famous doctor suspected
of kidnapping and murdering his wife

445
00:45:24.999 --> 00:45:28.335
flees questioning
and even steals from his in-laws…"

446
00:45:29.086 --> 00:45:31.171
That will definitely make the headline.

447
00:45:31.172 --> 00:45:32.672
And you have to really sell it.

448
00:45:32.673 --> 00:45:36.010
Make it look like you actually
kidnapped your own wife.

449
00:45:36.969 --> 00:45:40.389
You might have to do
more than just take the money.

450
00:45:41.891 --> 00:45:43.184
The three billion?

451
00:45:44.518 --> 00:45:46.937
So it was about money.

452
00:45:47.605 --> 00:45:49.315
Now I'm getting it.

453
00:45:50.149 --> 00:45:53.360
You got close to Seyun
for money from the start. right?

454
00:45:54.653 --> 00:45:56.613
See. honey? What did I tell you?

455
00:45:56.614 --> 00:45:59.283
I kept telling you that he was bad news.

456
00:46:00.284 --> 00:46:02.535
You're finally showing your true colors.

457
00:46:02.536 --> 00:46:05.205
You kept up the act pretty well. huh?

458
00:46:05.206 --> 00:46:06.707
What a performance!

459
00:46:07.625 --> 00:46:08.917
Taeju.

460
00:46:08.918 --> 00:46:12.170
If you want the money. let Seyun go first.

461
00:46:12.171 --> 00:46:14.172
Then I'll give you the money. All of it!

462
00:46:14.173 --> 00:46:15.216
No. Mother.

463
00:46:15.758 --> 00:46:18.426
Give me the money first.
That's the only way she'll live.

464
00:46:18.427 --> 00:46:19.595
What?

465
00:46:20.221 --> 00:46:24.098
You greedy bastard. Rot in hell!

466
00:46:24.099 --> 00:46:28.353
Taeju. How did you end up like this?

467
00:46:28.354 --> 00:46:30.146
Is this who you really are?

468
00:46:30.147 --> 00:46:35.026
I mean. this is just…
I can't believe this is happening.

469
00:46:35.027 --> 00:46:38.863
There's no point in talking
to this subhuman garbage.

470
00:46:38.864 --> 00:46:39.949
I'm calling the cops.

471
00:46:40.991 --> 00:46:42.201
I wouldn't do that. Father!

472
00:46:43.869 --> 00:46:45.078
"Father"?

473
00:46:45.079 --> 00:46:48.039
Don't you dare call me that!

474
00:46:48.040 --> 00:46:50.209
Have you no shame at all?

475
00:46:51.126 --> 00:46:52.544
I said don't do it!

476
00:46:53.045 --> 00:46:55.464
What? You're going to shoot me?

477
00:46:56.006 --> 00:46:58.342
Go on then. Shoot me!

478
00:46:59.301 --> 00:47:00.885
Shoot me. you bastard!

479
00:47:00.886 --> 00:47:03.388
Oh. honey. don't. Please. just…

480
00:47:03.389 --> 00:47:05.557
- You don't have the guts. do you?
- Please.

481
00:47:16.944 --> 00:47:19.363
Stop! Taeju!

482
00:47:20.114 --> 00:47:22.199
Please stop.

483
00:47:23.909 --> 00:47:25.494
Stay exactly where you are.

484
00:47:25.995 --> 00:47:27.704
Just take it!

485
00:47:27.705 --> 00:47:29.540
Please. just take the money!

486
00:47:41.468 --> 00:47:42.761
Go on. take it.

487
00:47:43.721 --> 00:47:44.805
Look at you.

488
00:47:45.639 --> 00:47:47.474
What would your mother say if she saw you?

489
00:47:48.976 --> 00:47:50.310
Is this what she gets

490
00:47:50.311 --> 00:47:54.231
for breaking her back all by herself.
trying to raise you right?

491
00:47:57.568 --> 00:47:58.569
Just answer me this.

492
00:48:01.071 --> 00:48:02.573
Is Seyun still alive?

493
00:48:04.825 --> 00:48:06.827
You could at least tell us that.

494
00:48:07.703 --> 00:48:09.204
Is she still alive?

495
00:48:12.458 --> 00:48:14.293
I believe so.

496
00:48:15.085 --> 00:48:16.086
What?

497
00:48:16.712 --> 00:48:19.757
What do you mean?

498
00:48:21.759 --> 00:48:22.760
Huh?

499
00:49:08.180 --> 00:49:11.266
LAW ENFORCEMENT

500
00:49:33.789 --> 00:49:36.792
Did he tell you anything
when he took the money?

501
00:49:38.127 --> 00:49:39.961
He was just here for the money.

502
00:49:39.962 --> 00:49:41.880
He even opened fire inside this house.

503
00:49:42.381 --> 00:49:44.465
He was in no state
to say anything sensible.

504
00:49:44.466 --> 00:49:46.635
And where have you people been?

505
00:49:47.845 --> 00:49:50.555
Are you even trying to catch this bastard?

506
00:49:50.556 --> 00:49:52.223
Well. we're doing everything we can.

507
00:49:55.060 --> 00:49:56.894
What if she dies?

508
00:49:56.895 --> 00:49:59.231
What if my daughter dies?

509
00:50:00.566 --> 00:50:02.484
What will you do then?

510
00:50:04.653 --> 00:50:06.864
He said he "believed so."

511
00:50:08.615 --> 00:50:09.866
Pardon?

512
00:50:09.867 --> 00:50:12.703
My husband asked him if Seyun was alive.

513
00:50:13.537 --> 00:50:15.706
and he said. "I believe so."

514
00:50:16.582 --> 00:50:18.667
Those were his words.

515
00:50:20.294 --> 00:50:21.295
He

516
00:50:22.713 --> 00:50:23.964
"believes so"?

517
00:50:36.226 --> 00:50:37.644
How are you?

518
00:50:40.856 --> 00:50:44.192
Wanted fugitive Kang Taeju.
who fled while being questioned

519
00:50:44.193 --> 00:50:46.986
over allegations of plotting
his wife's kidnapping and murder.

520
00:50:46.987 --> 00:50:50.072
is confirmed to have broken into
his in-laws' home early this morning

521
00:50:50.073 --> 00:50:52.742
and stolen billions of won in cash.

522
00:50:52.743 --> 00:50:54.911
Authorities say Kang fired
a stolen police weapon

523
00:50:54.912 --> 00:50:57.163
during the break-in
to threaten his parents-in-law.

524
00:50:57.164 --> 00:50:59.248
leaving the public in shock.

525
00:50:59.249 --> 00:51:01.375
Kang Taeju. a wanted fugitive

526
00:51:01.376 --> 00:51:02.835
and a prominent local neurosurgeon…

527
00:51:02.836 --> 00:51:05.880
Dr. Ha. did you see that?

528
00:51:05.881 --> 00:51:08.508
I knew something like this would happen.

529
00:51:08.509 --> 00:51:10.844
I told you he's crazy.
I knew he'd snap one day.

530
00:51:11.428 --> 00:51:12.846
That's not who he is.

531
00:51:13.931 --> 00:51:15.807
You're a terrible judge of character.

532
00:51:18.143 --> 00:51:19.478
Oh. look who it is.

533
00:51:20.103 --> 00:51:22.897
I heard they've been hitting it off
when he's on call.

534
00:51:22.898 --> 00:51:24.649
The rumors must be true.

535
00:51:25.776 --> 00:51:27.109
He's one of a kind.

536
00:51:27.110 --> 00:51:28.111
One of a kind indeed.

537
00:51:29.488 --> 00:51:30.489
Dr. Im.

538
00:51:31.740 --> 00:51:33.616
Things are already pretty tense right now.

539
00:51:33.617 --> 00:51:35.452
Don't go starting baseless rumors.

540
00:51:36.578 --> 00:51:38.621
Right. okay.

541
00:51:38.622 --> 00:51:41.499
Not only did police
carelessly lose track of the suspect.

542
00:51:41.500 --> 00:51:44.043
but authorities were virtually helpless

543
00:51:44.044 --> 00:51:46.462
as he scored a firearm right
in the heart of the city

544
00:51:46.463 --> 00:51:48.715
and went on to commit
another major offense.

545
00:51:49.883 --> 00:51:52.260
I was woken up by the loud blasts.

546
00:51:52.261 --> 00:51:54.470
I thought it was fireworks.

547
00:51:54.471 --> 00:51:57.181
Citizens are expressing
absolute terror over the fact that

548
00:51:57.182 --> 00:52:01.311
a violent criminal is actively roaming
the streets while armed with a gun.

549
00:52:16.201 --> 00:52:17.995
You made it onto the news.

550
00:52:20.998 --> 00:52:22.666
The culprit must've seen it too.

551
00:52:25.252 --> 00:52:27.169
CHOI HYEONSU
NATIONAL POLICE AGENCY

552
00:52:36.305 --> 00:52:39.808
REVEALING THE TRUTH
WITH THE POWER OF SCIENCE

553
00:52:45.063 --> 00:52:46.064
The NFS?

554
00:52:46.523 --> 00:52:48.900
You want me to go there? Why?

555
00:52:49.484 --> 00:52:51.612
To find the bait to lure him out.

556
00:53:00.787 --> 00:53:02.872
REQUEST FOR INVESTIGATION COOPERATION

557
00:53:02.873 --> 00:53:04.958
1. CASE NUMBER. 2026-9825
2. REQUESTED EVIDENCE

558
00:53:25.354 --> 00:53:29.357
Hi. I'm with Seongjin Police.
I'm here to urgently collect the evidence.

559
00:53:29.358 --> 00:53:31.360
Okay. give me a moment.

560
00:53:36.573 --> 00:53:37.783
Mmm. That's odd.

561
00:53:38.867 --> 00:53:40.952
I don't see anything in the system.

562
00:53:41.620 --> 00:53:42.703
Sorry?

563
00:53:42.704 --> 00:53:45.332
We should've received
an evidence release request first.

564
00:53:46.166 --> 00:53:47.167
Oh.

565
00:53:48.085 --> 00:53:51.213
No way. that's not possible.
We definitely sent in the form.

566
00:53:52.089 --> 00:53:53.757
Seongjin Police. right?

567
00:53:54.549 --> 00:53:57.426
Yeah. I'm with Seongjin Police.

568
00:53:57.427 --> 00:53:58.553
My name is Choi Hyeonsu.

569
00:54:14.736 --> 00:54:16.363
Hi. Chief. Are you busy?

570
00:54:17.280 --> 00:54:19.366
Yeah. I just want
to check something with you.

571
00:54:21.368 --> 00:54:24.246
Yeah. the case number is 2026-9825.

572
00:54:36.591 --> 00:54:39.051
Sir. where are you going?

573
00:54:39.052 --> 00:54:41.304
Oh. they caught that punk.

574
00:54:43.682 --> 00:54:46.059
- You're all clear.
- What?

575
00:54:46.935 --> 00:54:48.019
Your request.

576
00:54:48.937 --> 00:54:50.063
Ah.

577
00:54:50.605 --> 00:54:53.483
Looks like there was a hiccup
on your side of the system.

578
00:54:54.568 --> 00:54:55.776
I see.

579
00:54:55.777 --> 00:54:59.029
We still have to process it first.
but since you said it's urgent.

580
00:54:59.030 --> 00:55:00.657
I'll go grab the evidence for you.

581
00:55:02.325 --> 00:55:04.076
- How can I help you?
- Oh. hey.

582
00:55:04.077 --> 00:55:06.579
It's about case number 2026-5214.
A robbery case.

583
00:55:06.580 --> 00:55:08.497
{\an8}SUHYEONG
IT'S DONE

584
00:55:08.498 --> 00:55:09.666
It's done.

585
00:55:51.541 --> 00:55:52.625
Hungry. right?

586
00:55:57.756 --> 00:55:59.674
It's about time you got hungry.

587
00:56:02.135 --> 00:56:05.347
Well. I thought you would be.
so I grabbed some food.

588
00:56:13.563 --> 00:56:14.564
Take it.

589
00:56:16.358 --> 00:56:17.859
Come on. take it.

590
00:56:18.568 --> 00:56:22.614
Oh. right. I'm so stupid.
I forgot I tied your hands up.

591
00:56:23.615 --> 00:56:24.783
What do I do about that?

592
00:56:26.910 --> 00:56:30.705
So why did you do something so stupid?
Now I want to kill you.

593
00:56:38.713 --> 00:56:41.341
Ms. Ko. Listen.

594
00:56:42.175 --> 00:56:46.555
I know exactly what you're thinking
and doing. wherever you are.

595
00:57:07.284 --> 00:57:08.285
Right.

596
00:57:09.703 --> 00:57:11.371
Don't let the cream bun go to waste.

597
00:57:14.541 --> 00:57:15.750
Better eat it soon.

598
00:57:49.701 --> 00:57:50.702
Listen.

599
00:57:52.078 --> 00:57:56.541
I know exactly what you're thinking
and doing. wherever you are.

600
00:58:10.930 --> 00:58:13.350
RENOWNED NEUROSURGEON
INFILTRATES THE NFS

601
00:58:13.933 --> 00:58:17.061
What on earth is this guy doing? Geez…

602
00:58:46.549 --> 00:58:51.553
THE HUSBAND

603
00:59:31.594 --> 00:59:36.140
{\an8}It's three billion won. just as promised.
You're saying you don't want it. right?

604
00:59:36.141 --> 00:59:39.518
{\an8}Kang Taeju. you prick. I'm going
to make sure it's slow and painful.

605
00:59:39.519 --> 00:59:42.688
{\an8}There's not much time.

606
00:59:42.689 --> 00:59:45.315
{\an8}Don't react to him. Just wait.

607
00:59:45.316 --> 00:59:47.485
{\an8}That's the only way
you can save your wife.

608
00:59:48.820 --> 00:59:50.404
{\an8}No!

609
00:59:50.405 --> 00:59:51.489
{\an8}Get out of here!

610
00:59:52.323 --> 00:59:53.783
{\an8}This is the end of our deal.

611
00:59:54.534 --> 00:59:56.411
{\an8}Kang Taeju. stop!

612
00:59:58.955 --> 01:00:00.038
{\an8}Don't come close!

613
01:00:00.039 --> 01:00:02.458
{\an8}Mr. Kang. it's already over.

614
01:00:02.459 --> 01:00:03.543
{\an8}It's too late.

615
01:00:04.085 --> 01:00:06.087
{\an8}Translated by Hyun Sik Yoon
